snippet.title: RU77 game from MiroWin. Pre-teaser
snippet.description:
"RU77" game from MiroWin. Pre-teaser.

Welcome to discuss our future game on MiroWin Discord channel:
https://discord.com/invite/JYF49KX

The video uses the song "Black birds", composed by Nautilus Pompilius and covered by Alex Alpidovsky.
Alex Alpidovsky channel - https://www.youtube.com/c/AlpidovskyMusic
